        <div class="skill-box"><strong>Cloud:</strong> AWS, Terraform</div>
        <div class="skill-box"><strong>Database:</strong> MySQL</div>
        <div class="skill-box"><strong>Monitoring:</strong> Prometheus, Grafana</div>
