      <div class="edu">MSc ICT – University of Erlangen-Nuremberg (2022 – Present)</div>
      <div class="edu">B.E. Computer System Engineering – Mehran University (2014 – 2017)</div>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <h2>Certifications</h2>
      <div class="cert">• Certified Kubernetes Administrator (CKA)</div>
      <div class="cert">• HashiCorp Terraform Associate</div>
